original: Lindquist, Alva Maria, tandläkare, Linköping, f. 21/6/77 i Motala. — Mog:ex. v. Wallinska skolan i Sthlm 96, elev h. tandl. Edvard Olaison där 96-99, tandl :kand. 99, tandläkare 01. Praktik i Linköping sed. 01_, i Kisa somrarna 01-03. Sekr. i östergötl. läns tandl ifören. 14.
translated: Lindquist, Alva Maria, dentist, Linköping, b. 21/6/77 in Motala. - Married to Mr. Wallinska school in Stockholm in 1996, a student at Edvard Olaison dental school from 1996 to 1999, graduated as a dental student in 1999, became a dentist in 2001. Has been practicing in Linköping since 2001 and in Kisa during the summers of 2001-2003. Secretary in the Östergötland county dental association since 2014.
